_:N4364ace513e04b1ebb3d20404a4debcb <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Jamie is a passionate digital leader who likes to work with purpose, and inspire sustainable progress. A technology and innovation leader at heart who has spent the last 15 years driving digital transformation strategies to help customers navigate the sustainable energy transition.  In his current role as a global Digital Strategy Leader for Hitachi Energy, Jamie has spent the last seven years focussing on spearheading and evangelising a new sustainable energy era, enabled through advanced technologies such as IoT, AI/ML, and Edge computing.</p>\n" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
